    <id>http://ScottWeinstein.github.com/Recipes/blog/2012/12/30/sauerkraut</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2>Ingredient</h2>

<pre><code>* 3-4 Kg Cabbage
* 5 g salt/Kg cabbage

* 1 L water
* 15 g salt
</code></pre>

<h2>Steps</h2>

<pre><code>* Boil salt &amp; water, let cool
* Shred cabbage
* Mix salt and cabbage
* Pack tightly into crock
* Place stones
* Cover w/ salt water if required
* Cover w/ container and fill channel w/ salt water
* Wait 3-6 weeks
</code></pre>
